reviewText: The dvd was informative, but it was very out of date.  We did get some feeling of the culture and what too expect when we travel there

Incomplete DVD.  No travel in the Ticino, the Italian=speaking canton; nothing about Graubunden.  Nothing about the religions of the canton.  No photos of church or cathedral interiors.  Superficial DVD.  It should be removed from Amazon's catalog.
